Package domain

Class QuadraticEquation

java.lang.Object
domain.QuadraticEquation
public class QuadraticEquation extends Object

Class:
QuadraticEquation.

Description:
The QuadraticEquation class represents a quadratic equation with coefficients for the terms ax^2 + bx + c. It provides methods to set and get the coefficients, calculate the solutions, and retrieve the solutions as complex numbers.

Control change:

  • 0.1.0: Create class.

Since:
0.1.0
